  "repo_truth": "Fresh read-only Review 6 of the exact seventeen-entry HCM-2.1 planning subject after five bounded findings/remediation rounds. Review 5 found the last static selected-path carrier in AuthorProjectContextResult and the legacy fixed path export. Parent docs-only remediation makes the author result path an owned String supplied only from the selected decision and deletes the legacy constant/re-exports without alias. Independently revalidate all prior findings and complete live implementability; inherit no clean conclusion.",
  "allowed_scope": [
    "Remain read-only and replay the sorted seventeen-entry manifest and aggregate fingerprint before review.",
    "Review every byte of 00, 04, 06, HCM-2.1 SPEC, plan, unchecked todo, all six planning proof files, and immutable Review 1 through Review 5 dispatches.",
    "Read Review 1 cited live engine/compiler/flow/CLI/template/fixture/test sources and unchanged 01, 02, 03, 05, 07, 08, HCM-0.6 decision, selected HCM-1.4 record, and definition assets only as needed.",
    "Run bounded read-only Markdown, link, Git, handoff/schema, source/API feasibility, DTO/byte-contract, cross-platform, compatibility, determinism, security, and proof checks.",
    "Return findings first with exact file/line evidence through the built-in channel."
  ],
  "non_goals": [
    "No edits, staging, commits, new dispatches, global handoffs, ledger writes, or user task hops.",
    "No Rust, Cargo, definition, template, fixture, test, runtime/product, pipeline, HCM-2.2+, SDK, Tauri, Substrate, contract, dock, or publication implementation.",
    "Do not invent an alternative remediation, schema field, compatibility mode, serializer, renderer rule, observation model, DTO, budget domain, platform guarantee, Environment Inventory conversion, or pipeline migration.",
    "Do not treat any prior review, remediation proof, baseline test, or contingent status wording as evidence that the seventeen-entry subject is clean."
  ],
  "tasks": [
    "Invoke required skills in order, remain read-only, replay the exact seventeen-entry manifest/aggregate, and return BLOCKED if any byte differs.",
    "Review findings first in Critical, Required, Optional, Nit order with exact evidence, gate, failure, smallest remediation, and invalidated proof.",
    "Revalidate all fourteen prior Required findings and five remediation rounds against live source and cross-document truth.",
    "Verify AuthorProjectContextResult owns the selected decision path, legacy fixed path constant/re-exports are deleted without alias, and author core/shell/API/CLI/file/stdin proof is complete.",
    "Verify all earlier engine identity/freshness, flow/compiler carrier, C04, CLI setup reason, Environment Inventory, observation/ABA, deterministic bytes, DTO/budget/log, and non-Unix contracts remain total.",
    "Verify outcome-neutral status, docs-only scope, unchecked todo, bridge/classification ceiling, staged GitNexus, primary commit, and separate handoff/ledger closeout.",
    "Return CLEAN only if no valid Critical or Required finding remains; otherwise CHANGES_REQUIRED or BLOCKED. Make no edits and use bounded checks."
  ],
